=== Listing ===

* list files in current directory

<pre>ls</pre>

* list all files

<pre>ls -a</pre>

* list all files with related informations in columns

<pre>ls -al</pre>

* list all files with their sizes are human readable format

<pre> ls -alh</pre>

* list all files sorted according to their sizes

<pre> ls -alhS</pre>

* list all files sorted according to last modified dates

<pre> ls -alht</pre>
